data.eml:eml: New species of darkling beetles (Coleoptera: Tenebrionidae) from San Salvador Island, Bahamas

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Steiner, Warren E., Jr (2006): New species of darkling beetles (Coleoptera: Tenebrionidae) from San Salvador Island, Bahamas. Zootaxa 1158: 1-38, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.172291
